<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Payment Success - Travel Manager</title>
    <style>
        /* Votre CSS associ√© ici */
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f7f7f7;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .header img {
            max-width: 150px;
        }
        
        .content {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .invoice {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .invoice-title {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .invoice-details {
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }
        
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #007bff;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <img src="{{url}}/next.svg" alt="Travel Manager Logo">
            <h1>Payment Successful - Travel Manager</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear {{reciever}},</p>
            <p>We are happy to inform you that your payment for the following services has been successfully processed:</p>
            <div class="invoice">
                <h2 class="invoice-title">Invoice #{{invoiceNumber}}</h2>
                <p class="invoice-details">
                    <strong>Date:</strong> {{invoiceDate}}<br>
                    <strong>Amount:</strong> {{invoiceAmount}}<br>
                    <strong>Payment Method:</strong> {{paymentMethod}}
                </p>
            </div>
            <p>Thank you for using Travel Manager for your travel needs. If you have any questions or need further assistance, feel free to contact our support team.</p>
            <p>Happy travels!</p>
            <p>
                <a href="{{url}}/signin" class="cta-button">SignIn</a>
            </p>
            <p>If you need a copy of your invoice, you can download it from your account settings.</p>
            <p>Best regards,</p>
            <p>The Travel Manager Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
